<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="26Apr1937"><font color="red">26 April 1937</font> <i>NLJL</i> (from G. Wren Howard to Paul L&eacute;on): I have just arranged for a specially qualified reader to compare the Albatross edition, copy of which I brought here with me from Paris, with the John Lane 3 Guinea edition. </div>
